 time, the BEV\nand MLS method are preferred. We recommend to use the four methods together, in\norder to best identify the location and cause of the activity changes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Oct 2022 11:41:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2022 17:37:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
